パッケージ com.github.siroshun09.configapi.common

インタフェース Configuration

既知のサブインタフェースのリスト:
FileConfiguration, Yaml
既知の実装クラスのリスト:
BukkitConfig, BukkitYaml, BungeeConfig, BungeeYaml
public interface Configuration
An interface that gets the value by path.

Using null for @NotNull argument will cause a NullPointerException.

    • getBoolean

      boolean getBoolean​(@NotNull @NotNull String path)
      Gets the requested boolean by path.

      If the value could not be obtained, this method returns false.

      パラメータ:
      path - Path of the boolean to get.
      戻り値:
      Requested boolean.

      @NotNull @NotNull Collection<String> getKeys()

    • set

      void set​(@NotNull @NotNull String path, @Nullable @Nullable Object value)
      Set the value to the specified path.

      If given value is null, the path will be removed.

      パラメータ:
      path - Path of the object to set.
      value - New value to set the path to.
